Yes by God it's dust.

142
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:02,000
Av mala xalê...?
 
Is this uncle... house?

143
00:14:02,000 --> 00:14:04,000
Mala Hesen...
 
Hesen's house...

144
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:09,000
