151
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:35,000
Av mala Ednê ne?
 
Is this Ednê's house?

152
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:55,000
Erê.
 
Yes.

153
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:04,000
